          <div class="d-flex align-items-end">
            <button type="button" class="profile-edit-btn ms-1" id="editButton">編輯個人資料</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="name-account-container d-flex flex-column bd-highlight p-1 ms-3">
          <a href="" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="profile-name">崎玉</div>
          </a>
          <a href="" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="profile-account">@yahoo</div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-follow col" style="max-width: 100%;">
          <p class="profile-intro mx-4">
            原為一個失業的普通上班族，在遇到怪人蟹爪蘭蒂並且打敗他救了孩子之後，決定成為英雄。
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-start mx-4">
            <div>
              <a href=" " class="text-decoration-none" style="margin-right: 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px">
                <span style="color: #171725;">22 個</span>
                <span style="color: #6C757D;">跟隨中</span>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a href=" " class="text-decoration-none" style="margin-right: 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px">
                <span style="color: #171725;">33 個</span>
                <span style="color: #6C757D;">跟隨者</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

